OL,3,CGreens win by-election to replace
OL,4,Cjailed Reform councillor
OL,6,FThe Green Party has won a Kent County
OL,7,FCouncil by-election, called after a
OL,8,Fserving councillor was jailed.
OL,10,FDaniel Taylor, 35, from Margate, was
OL,11,Fsuspended by Reform shortly after he
OL,12,Fwon the Cliftonville ward during local
OL,13,Felections in 2025.
OL,15,FHe sat as an independent until he was
OL,16,Fgiven a 12-month prison sentence in
OL,17,FFebruary, after he admitted to
OL,18,Fbehaving in a controlling and coercive
OL,19,Fway towards his wife.
