OL,3,CGreens win by-election to replace
OL,4,Cjailed Reform councillor
OL,6,FReacting to the loss of the by-
OL,7,Felection on Friday, a Reform UK
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "Marc and the team
OL,9,Fhave run an incredible, positive and
OL,10,Fprofessional campaign in the midst of
OL,11,Fchallenging circumstances.
OL,13,F"We'd like to thank voters for their
OL,14,Fsupport. The overriding message from
OL,15,Fthis result is, vote Conservative, get
OL,16,FGreen."
OL,18,FThe full results were as follows:
